[normal]Appendix 2[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]Extracts from [bold]The current and future UK science workforce[bold]Report prepared for the Science Council by TBR, 2011 [bold]&#xa0;
[normal]This research uses a new analysis
[normal] considering the science workforce across the entire economy, rather than looking at total employees within science based industries. This innovative approach enables an understanding of the true size and scope of the science workforce across the economy, 
[normal]rather than limiting the research to considering scientists working in a narrow band of science sectors.
[normal]&#xa0;
